  {'id': 'hl003', 'text': 'To keep the body in good health is a duty... otherwise we shall not be able to keep our mind strong and clear.', 'author': 'Gautama Buddha', 'category': 'health'},
  {'id': 'hl004', 'text': 'A healthy outside starts from the inside.', 'author': 'Robert Urich', 'category': 'health'},
  {'id': 'hl005', 'text': 'Physical fitness is not only one of the most important keys to a healthy body, it is the basis of dynamic and creative intellectual activity.', 'author': 'John F. Kennedy', 'category': 'health'},
